plans.name: Single Ride
plans.description: Includes one bike for one trip up to 30 minutes. $20 fee for ending trip out of system area applies.

plans.name: Day Pass
plans.description: 24-hour access starting on same day of purchase. Additional bikes billed at $0.10/min. Free time applies to first bike only. $20 fee for ending trip out of system area applies.

plans.name: Annual Member
plans.description: $12 / month with an annual commitment. Additional bikes billed at $0.10/min. Free time applies to first bike only. $20 fee for ending trip out of system area applies.
